Game Group to Name Former Ladbrokes CEO as Chairman, Times Says

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-04-10T15:28:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-10/game-group-to-name-former-ladbrokes-ceo-as-chairman-times-says.html
Game Group Plc (GMG) , a U.K. electronic
games retailer, plans to name former  Ladbrokes Plc (LAD)  Chief
Executive Officer Chris Bell as chairman, the Sunday Times
 reported , without saying where it got the information.  Bell served as interim chief executive officer at Game
Group last year, the report said.  Game Group could not immediately be reached by telephone
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London at 
 rgraham13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  